headline: AIG to Report Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2025 Financial Results on February 10, 2026, and Host Conference Call on February 11, 2026
summary: NEW YORK, January 16, 2026--American International Group, Inc. (NYSE: AIG) will report financial results for the fourth quarter and full year ended December 31, 2025, after the market closes on Tuesday, February 10, 2026. AIG’s press release and financial supplement will be available in the Investors section of AIG’s website at https://www.aig.com.
